name: Figma Chicago Art Gallery Walk (April 2020)
description:
This is the final art gallery walk from the Figma Chicago April 2020 meetup event. We created a set of art prompts to follow, and attendees spent a couple hours creating art and listening to music together, virtually! 

Enjoy perusing the gallery, or duplicate this file and use it to host your own event!

Remixable file for the art template is available here: https://www.figma.com/community/file/839503396119450890/Community-Art-Frame
